    "summary": "This section addresses the strategic revitalization of legacy gaming products via mini-game platforms. It can answer retrieval queries concerning:\n- **Topics/Claims:** Product lifecycle extension and renewal strategies for older titles through WeChat Mini Games.\n- **Entities:** WeChat Mini Games (distribution platform) and DianDian (copyright holder).\n- **Dates:** 2016 (original Chinese server launch) and Q4 2025 (WeChat Mini Games release).\n- **Procedures/Features:** User data migration and synchronization protocols, specifically confirming original data retention and cross-platform (dual-end) interoperability.\n- **Evidence/Format:** Presentation slide content (pages 37-38) with corporate copyright metadata, functioning as a strategic announcement or roadmap update. No tables, figures, definitions, or quantitative metrics are present."
